かまのような、お<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">三</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>か<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">月</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">づき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">早</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はよ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>う、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">大</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おお</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>きくなって、<lb />
お<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">嫁入</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よめい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">晩</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ばん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、<lb />
まるい<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">顔</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かお</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>して、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">雲</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のあいから、のぞいてみい。<lb />
<lb />
